title: Jazzy Bach - Goldberg Variations - Stuttgart Chamber Orchestra,
description:
This awesome jazz CD contains Bach's Goldberg Variations performed first in classic style by the Stuttgart Chamber Orchestra, then recomposed as a jazz interpretation on the next track by Kalman Olah and Mini Schulz.
